Text: Followup Originator Support Cc Ladies As a followup to yesterdays request I have included a spreadsheet that may help clarify the specific data our originators are looking for Also I found a regional Capacity Report from RISI hard copy If you have any further questions feel free to contact me Thanks Laura Laura E Bosek Analyst Enron Industrial Markets ext

Originator Support Cc Dear Team Our originators are in need of regional market information They are in search of capacity and consumption data for three regions North America AsiaPacific and Europe The problem were facing is that each publication is disclosing very different numbers I think RISI is the publication which contains the most data across these commodities If RISI data is not available for your commodity please send me any data that is available Also please disclose units if possible The information requested is for a presentation for Ray Bowen this week The following is this presentation If you have any further questions please contact me Thanks for all your help Regards Laura Laura E Bosek Analyst Enron Industrial Markets ext
